&lt;p&gt;auctions_path links to the index of all auctions&lt;br&gt;
auction_path(Auction.first) would link to a specific auction&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;link_to is also smart about models so you could use link_to
&quot;Test&quot;, auction&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
